{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was over-- over, you know, 6 foot, so that's-- he didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the-- still the cemetery was still intact, so he had a Jewish burial.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the rabbi was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quickly because Rosh Hashanah was-- was the eve of Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It feel that my sister got so very sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She held it more than my mother because my mother had to help us to get over it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then it wasn't long after, we were taken away to that camp-- to that labor camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two [? months-- ?] October, the 22nd of October.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Labor camp, Staw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-T-A-W.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a very big mill, and we were-- they-- we were housed there, in the mill.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About 700-- 700 people were housed in that mill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was, again, very hard work there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mostly the same thing, but we were working at home and at [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mogilanka ?] River.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes [? other ?] things, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, by Germans, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the Germans, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they didn't beat us up or something like that, but the-- the food, we-- we didn't get much to eat, only the morning some bread and maybe coffee.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called it coffee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we were coming home, there was a bit of soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was an incident in December.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is something that I don't know how to get it out to my mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were standing-- it is Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a Sunday, and we were not working on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to get everything like ready to get clean to-- to wash your bed and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't very easy, but to somehow we tried, you know, with snow to melt snow if there wasn't enough water.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
